[{"index":1,"title":"【诗词】永远的天堂","content":"永远的天堂&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;亲爱的&nbsp;不要忧伤&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>我会用我的思念&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>做你的翅膀&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>飞吧&nbsp;飞向你要去的方向&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>掌纹构筑的年轮&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>记载不了多少沧桑&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>夜雨&nbsp;沙沙的响&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>不会再打湿你的天窗&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>北方的沙漠&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>没有我的心更荒凉&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>而我的心房&nbsp;为你&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>愿意把所有的风雨遮挡&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>可以吗&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>给我一片温柔的树叶&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>潮汐再起的时候&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>还可以在海边眺望&nbsp;&nbsp;\u0018","author":"清水§芙蓉","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.9f2b0776.vDOQfGBzyUlyWcL_1rdZPg&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-08 19:44","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":2,"title":"回复：【诗词】永远的天堂","content":"D","author":null,"author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-08 19:47","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":3,"title":"回复：【诗词】永远的天堂","content":"继续努力~�","author":"雪￡魅儿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.ec7c4b5f.KSJNpCIUJLOmFrJ1VJmBpQ&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-08 19:51","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":4,"title":"回复：【诗词】永远的天堂","content":"交个朋友","author":"梦幻☆灵儿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.1a856757.CvCTctl0jF7ndGgRlEroFw&fr=pb","date":"2006-08-02 11:46","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null}]